---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About - RANDOBLOG" description="Learn about the person behind RANDOBLOG – a self-proclaimed wannabe scientist with questionable lab safety habits and big dreams">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">

        <!-- Main content -->
        <div class="space-y-12">
            <!-- Mission Statement -->
            <section class="card">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-semibold text-text-primary mb-6">
                    What is RANDOBLOG?
                </h2>
                <div class="space-y-4 text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
                    <p>
                        RANDOBLOG is where I pour my over-caffeinated curiosity into pixels. It’s an ever-shifting collection of ideas, experiments, and rabbit holes I’ve fallen into – ranging from physics and computer science to “what happens if I mix these two entirely unrelated concepts and hope it doesn’t explode.”
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Think of it as my digital notebook-slash-laboratory, except without the risk of spilling acid on my shoes (again). I may not have a Nobel Prize (yet, or ever), but I’m here for the joy of exploration, a pinch of absurdity, and the occasional “Eureka!” moment that usually turns out to be me rediscovering something from 1893.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- About Me -->
            <section class="card">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-semibold text-text-primary mb-6">
                    About Me
                </h2>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                    <div class="p-4 bg-bg-tertiary rounded-lg border border-accent-primary/20 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md hover:border-accent-primary/30 transition-all duration-200">
                        <div class="text-accent-primary font-medium mb-2">
                            Academic Credentials
                        </div>
                        <div class="text-text-secondary text-sm">
                            None that would impress a hiring committee, but I own a suspicious number of lab coats.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-4 bg-bg-tertiary rounded-lg border border-accent-secondary/20 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md hover:border-accent-secondary/30 transition-all duration-200">
                        <div class="text-accent-secondary font-medium mb-2">
                            Experimental Skills
                        </div>
                        <div class="text-text-secondary text-sm">
                            Adept at pushing buttons I probably shouldn’t and Googling “is it supposed to smoke like that?”
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-4 bg-bg-tertiary rounded-lg border border-accent-primary/20 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md hover:border-accent-primary/30 transition-all duration-200">
                        <div class="text-accent-primary font-medium mb-2">
                            Scientific Focus
                        </div>
                        <div class="text-text-secondary text-sm">
                            Whatever currently keeps me awake at 2 AM – quantum weirdness, black holes, or why my coffee tastes metallic.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-4 bg-bg-tertiary rounded-lg border border-accent-secondary/20 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md hover:border-accent-secondary/30 transition-all duration-200">
                        <div class="text-accent-secondary font-medium mb-2">
                            Long-Term Goal
                        </div>
                        <div class="text-text-secondary text-sm">
                            To someday be mistaken for an actual scientist in a dimly lit conference hallway.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- Features -->
            <section class="card">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-semibold text-text-primary mb-6">
                    Key Features of This Blog
                </h2>
                <p class="text-text-secondary mb-8">
                    In case you’re wondering what you’ve stumbled into:
                </p>

                <div class="space-y-8">
                    <div class="p-6 bg-bg-tertiary rounded-lg border border-accent-primary/20 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md hover:border-accent-primary/30 transition-all duration-200">
                        <div class="text-accent-primary font-medium mb-3">Mathematical Content:</div>
                        <p class="text-text-secondary">
                            Supports full LaTeX rendering, because math is beautiful… even when I’m using it to prove something completely trivial.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="p-6 bg-bg-tertiary rounded-lg border border-accent-secondary/20 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md hover:border-accent-secondary/30 transition-all duration-200">
                        <div class="text-accent-secondary font-medium mb-3">Live Content:</div>
                        <p class="text-text-secondary">
                            Automatically synced from GitHub so my bad ideas update in real time.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <div class="p-6 bg-bg-tertiary rounded-lg border border-accent-primary/20 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md hover:border-accent-primary/30 transition-all duration-200">
                        <div class="text-accent-primary font-medium mb-3">Research Focus:</div>
                        <p class="text-text-secondary">
                            Physics, AI, space stuff, and anything else that lets me pretend I’m in a sci-fi movie.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- CTA -->
            <section class="text-center">
                <div class="card">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-semibold text-text-primary mb-6">
                        Ready to explore?
                    </h2>
                    <p class="text-text-secondary mb-8">
                        Enter the chaos. It’s educational… probably.
                    </p>
                    <a href="/" class="btn-primary">
                        View Posts
                    </a>
                </div>
            </section>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- KaTeX CSS and JS -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.8/dist/katex.min.css" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <script defer src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.8/dist/katex.min.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script defer src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.8/dist/contrib/auto-render.min.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

    <!-- Initialize KaTeX auto-render -->
    <script>
        document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() {
            if (typeof renderMathInElement !== 'undefined') {
                renderMathInElement(document.body, {
                    delimiters: [
                        {left: '$$', right: '$$', display: true},
                        {left: '$', right: '$', display: false}
                    ],
                    throwOnError: false
                });
            }
        });
    </script>
</Layout>
